<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-develop-new-ai-tools-to-reveal-seizure-hotspots-improve-patient-care/">Mayo Clinic researchers develop new AI tools to reveal seizure hotspots, improve patient care</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
