<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-researchers-study-stool-to-unlock-microbiomes-role-in-cancer-treatment/">Mayo researchers study stool to unlock microbiome&amp;#8217;s role in cancer treatment&nbsp;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
